      "date": "2011-05-12 16:49:08.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 5.6/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/6b7e8fde-7cb7-11e0-b5bf-52540025f9af).  Ran 1 tests.  No failures.",
